                            <h1 class="card-title mt-0 fs-1">THE STUDENT PARTICIPATION RECORD</h1>
                            <p class="card-text">On the dashboard, simply click on the “Records” button to hop into the
                                Student Participation Record page, or you can immediately search for it
                                by using the search bar and entering either the student’s name or ID!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
